#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing &plasma-desktop; and &kde; Applications"
msgstr "&plasma-desktop संस्थापनम्; तथा &kde; अनुप्रयोगाः"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install &kde; applications, including &plasma-desktop;, on a variety "
"of different platforms, ranging from smartphones and tablets to computers "
"running &Microsoft; &Windows;, &macOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD; or &Linux;. Binary "
"packages are available for many different platforms and distributions, or "
"advanced users may build the source code."
msgstr ""
"भवान् &kde; अनुप्रयोगाः, यथा &plasma-desktop;, विविधविभिन्नमञ्चेषु, स्मार्टफोन-टैब्लेट्-"
"तः आरभ्य &Microsoft; &Windows;, &macOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD;,अथवा &Linux; "
"द्विचक्रीयसङ्कुलाः अनेकविधमञ्चानां वितरणानाञ्च कृते उपलभ्यन्ते, अथवा उन्नतप्रयोक्तारः "
"स्रोतसङ्केतं निर्मातुम् अर्हन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Packages"
msgstr "संकुलं संस्थापनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hundreds of developers worldwide have done a lot of work to make it easy to "
"install &kde; onto a variety of different devices and platforms."
msgstr "विश्वे शतशः विकासकाः &kde; विविधविविधयन्त्राणां मञ्चानां च उपरि ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Linux;"
msgstr "&लिनक्स;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Nearly every &Linux; distribution provides binary packages for individual "
"applications and the &plasma-desktop; as a whole."
msgstr ""
"प्रायः प्रत्येकं &Linux; वितरणं व्यक्तिगत-अनुप्रयोगानाम् कृते द्विचक्रीय-सङ्कुलं प्रदाति तथा च "
"&plasma-desktop; समग्ररूपेण ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install an individual application, look for its name in your "
"distribution's package collection. To install one of the &plasma-"
"workspaces;, like &plasma-desktop;, look for a metapackage or package group, "
"typically <literal>plasma-desktop</literal>."
msgstr ""
"व्यक्तिगतं अनुप्रयोगं संस्थापयितुं, स्वस्य वितरणस्य संकुलसङ्ग्रहे तस्य नाम अन्वेष्टुम् । &plasma-"
"workspaces;-मध्ये एकं संस्थापयितुं, &plasma-desktop;, मेटापैकेज अथवा संकुलसमूहं अन्वेष्टुम्, "
"सामान्यतया <literal>plasma-desktop</literal>"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some applications may be installed together with other applications in a "
"combined package named after the &kde; package they are provided in. For "
"instance, &konqueror; might be found in the <literal>kde-baseapps</literal> "
"package."
msgstr ""
"केचन अनुप्रयोगाः अन्यैः अनुप्रयोगैः सह &kde; संकुलं ते प्रदत्ताः सन्ति यथा, &konqueror; "
"<literal>kde-baseapps</literal> संकुलमध्ये द्रष्टुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have trouble locating &kde; packages for your distribution, please "
"contact their support resources. Many distributions also have a team "
"dedicated to packaging applications by &kde; that can provide assistance "
"specific to them."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतः स्थाननिर्धारणे कष्टं भवति &kde; संकुलं भवतः वितरणार्थं, कृपया तेषां समर्थनसम्पदां "
"सम्पर्कं कुर्वन्तु। अनेकवितरणानाम् अपि &kde; यत् तेषां विशिष्टं साहाय्यं दातुं शक्नोति।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Microsoft; &Windows;"
msgstr "&माइक्रोसॉफ्ट; &विण्डोज;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kde; on Windows Initiative provides binary packages of &kde; "
"applications for &Microsoft; &Windows;. They also provide a special "
"installer application that permits you to install individual applications or "
"groups and all necessary dependencies easily."
msgstr ""
"इति &kde; on Windows Initiative इत्यनेन &kde; &Microsoft; &विण्डोज;। ते एकं विशेषं "
"संस्थापक-अनुप्रयोगं अपि प्रदास्यन्ति यत् भवन्तं व्यक्तिगत-अनुप्रयोगं वा समूहं वा सर्वाणि "
"आवश्यकानि आश्रयाणि च सुलभतया संस्थापयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on the initiative and to download the installer, visit "
"<ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Windows\">the KDE on Windows "
"Initiative</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"उपक्रमस्य विषये अधिकसूचनार्थं संस्थापकस्य अवतरणं कर्तुं च <ulink url=\"https://community."
"kde.org/Windows\">विण्डोज उपक्रमे KDE</ulink> इति पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "&macOS;"
msgstr "&macOS;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Individual &kde; applications can be installed through several different "
"<quote>ports</quote> systems available for &macOS;. Several different &kde; "
"applications also provide their own binary builds for &macOS;."
msgstr ""
"व्यक्तिगत &kde; अनुप्रयोगाः &macOS;-कृते उपलभ्यमानानां अनेकानाम् <quote>पोर्ट्</quote>-"
"प्रणालीनां माध्यमेन संस्थापनं कर्तुं शक्यन्ते । अनेकाः भिन्नाः &kde; अनुप्रयोगाः &macOS;-कृते "
"स्वकीयानि द्विचक्रीय-निर्माणानि अपि प्रदास्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, visit <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Mac"
"\">&kde; on &macOS;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"अधिकविवरणार्थं <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Mac\">&kde; &macOS;X</"
"ulink> इत्यत्र ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "&BSD;"
msgstr "&BSD;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most &BSD; distributions allows you to install &kde; applications and the "
"&plasma-desktop; through their <quote>ports</quote> system."
msgstr ""
"अधिकांशः &BSD; distributions भवन्तं &kde; अनुप्रयोगाः तथा &plasma-desktop; तेषां "
"<quote>पोर्ट्</quote> प्रणाल्याः माध्यमेन ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on installing ports, see your &BSD; distribution's "
"documentation."
msgstr "पोर्ट् संस्थापनविषये अधिकविवरणार्थं स्वस्य &BSD; वितरणस्य दस्तावेजीकरणम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mobile Devices"
msgstr "मोबाईल उपकरण"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<productname>Plasma Mobile</productname> is an exciting initiative to bring "
"a new &kde; experience to mobile devices like smartphones or tablets. Binary "
"releases are provided for several different devices."
msgstr ""
"<productname>प्लाज्मा मोबाईल</productname> इति नूतनं &kde; स्मार्टफोन-टैब्लेट्-"
"इत्यादीनां मोबाईल-उपकरणानाम् अनुभवः । अनेकविभिन्नयन्त्राणां कृते द्विचक्रीयविमोचनं प्रदत्तम् "
"अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, visit <ulink url=\"https://www.plasma-mobile.org/"
"\"><productname>Plasma Mobile</productname></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"अधिकविवरणार्थं <ulink url=\"https://www.plasma-mobile.org/"
"\"><productname>प्लाज्मा मोबाईल</productname></ulink> इति सञ्चिकां पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Live Media"
msgstr "लाइव मीडिया"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several &Linux; and &BSD; distributions offer live media. This permits you "
"to try out the &plasma-desktop; without installing anything to your system. "
"All you have to do insert a CD or connect a USB drive and boot from it. If "
"you like what you see, most offer an option to install it to your hard drive."
msgstr ""
"अनेकाः &Linux; तथा &BSD; वितरणं लाइव मीडिया प्रदाति। एतेन भवन्तः &plasma-desktop; "
"भवतः प्रणाल्यां किमपि संस्थापनं विना। भवद्भिः केवलं CD सम्मिलितं कुर्वन्तु अथवा USB ड्राइव् "
"संयोजयित्वा तस्मात् बूट् कुर्वन्तु । यदि भवन्तः यत् पश्यन्ति तत् रोचन्ते तर्हि अधिकांशः भवतः "
"हार्डड्राइव् मध्ये संस्थापनस्य विकल्पं प्रददति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\">a "
"list of distributions that offer the &kde; workspace and applications on "
"live media</ulink> on the &kde; website."
msgstr ""
"तत्र <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\">वितरणानां "
"सूची अस्ति ये &kde; कार्यक्षेत्रं तथा लाइव मीडिया</ulink> इत्यत्र अनुप्रयोगाः &kde; "
"website."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Building from Source Code"
msgstr "स्रोतसंहितातः निर्माणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For detailed information on how to compile and install &plasma-desktop; and "
"applications see <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Guidelines_and_HOWTOs/Build_from_source\">Build from source</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&plasma-desktop; तथा अनुप्रयोगाः <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Guidelines_and_HOWTOs/Build_from_source\">स्रोतः निर्माणं</ulink> पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &kde; software uses <command>cmake</command> you should have no "
"trouble compiling it. Should you run into problems please report them to the "
"&kde; mailing lists."
msgstr ""
"यतः &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर <command>cmake</command> इत्यस्य उपयोगं करोति भवद्भिः तस्य संकलने "
"कोऽपि कष्टः न भवितुमर्हति । यदि भवान् समस्यां प्राप्नोति तर्हि कृपया तान् &kde; "
"मेलसूचिकाः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The recommended tool to build Frameworks, &plasma-desktop; and all the other "
"applications is <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/kdesrc-build\">kdesrc-"
"build</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Frameworks इत्यस्य निर्माणार्थं अनुशंसितं साधनं, &plasma-desktop; तथा अन्ये सर्वे "
"अनुप्रयोगाः <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/kdesrc-build\">kdesrc-build</"
"ulink> इति"
